          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "Light and shadows morph strangely around the bul-gae. Non-magical bright light is reduced to dim light within the aura. When a creature attempts an action within the aura that has the light trait, it must attempt a DC 34 Will save. On a failure, the action is disrupted.",
